---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="About — Deskbly" description="Who we are and why we started Deskbly." />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>About Deskbly</h1>
			<p>
				We started Deskbly because buying home office furniture online is a mess. 
				Every "review" site is just rewritten Amazon descriptions with affiliate links. 
				Nobody actually helps you decide.
			</p>
			<p>
				We're different. We research every product we recommend, compare specs honestly, 
				and tell you when something isn't worth the money — even if it means we don't 
				earn a commission.
			</p>
			<h2>What We Cover</h2>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Standing desks & sit-stand desks</strong> — from budget to premium</li>
				<li><strong>Ergonomic chairs</strong> — for every budget and body type</li>
				<li><strong>Monitors & monitor arms</strong> — because your neck matters</li>
				<li><strong>Keyboards, mice & accessories</strong> — the small upgrades that make a big difference</li>
				<li><strong>Setup inspiration</strong> — real desk setups with real budgets</li>
			</ul>
			<h2>Our Promise</h2>
			<p>
				Some links on this site are affiliate links — we earn a small commission if you buy 
				through them, at no extra cost to you. This is how we keep the site running. 
				But it never influences our recommendations. If a product sucks, we'll say so.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
